### Get Available Slots
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/available-slots?date=2023-10-01&serviceTypeId=123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### Get Calendar View
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/calendar

### Create Appointment
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
  "vehicleId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001",
  "serviceTypeId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174002",
  "appointmentDate": "2023-10-01",
  "appointmentTime": "10:00:00",
  "notes": "Regular maintenance",
  "assignedStaffId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174003"
}

### Get All Appointments
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/

### Get Appointment by ID
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### Update Appointment
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
  "vehicleId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001",
  "serviceTypeId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174002",
  "appointmentDate": "2023-10-02",
  "appointmentTime": "11:00:00",
  "notes": "Updated maintenance",
  "assignedStaffId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174003"
}

### Cancel Appointment
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### Update Appointment Status
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CONFIRMED",
  "notes": "Appointment confirmed",
  "changedByStaffId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174003",
  "invoiceAmount": 50.00,
  "invoiceDetails": "Oil change service"
}

### Get Appointment Status Log
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/status-log

### Get Tracking Appointments
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/tracking?status=PENDING